Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, the garden is also huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.34,0:02:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True, true!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, the night will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.83,0:02:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! We didn't come to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Control yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of you all, look at Miru's calmness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ino-chan, cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It even has a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rules?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In case of quitting, you'll be disqualified from Lemon Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a Miki joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, Miki thinks that's absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need girls that don't try hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, he's arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll introduce him, this is the new music director for Lemon Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Katagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to the company, so obey Katagiri-san's instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the training schedule.
