Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the training schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up at 4am, run, abdominals, crouch, then coffee and dance class?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:29.44,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}7:00 - Morning Coffee | - Menu: Rice, Fish, Soup | 8:00 - Dance Class: Capoeira,  Rock, Jazz | 12:00 - Lunch |\N - Menu: Rice, Hamburger, Salad, Soup | 13:00 - Dance Class: Hip-Hop, Street Dance, Cossack | 17:00 - Bath
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing vocal exercises during all training.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:33.44,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}18:00 - Dinner | - Menu: - Bread, Mixed Eggs, Salad, Orange Juice | 19:00 - Body building | \N20:00 - Sleep | Do exactly as the menu says. | The use of cell phones and text messaging is forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... it's too hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think with actual techniques you could record something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll train correctly until I say it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ehhh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anybody has any complaints, leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we stop doing the activities, we'll be disqualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick up your bags and get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.37,0:03:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will they be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll keep up for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he accepted that role easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell the truth, it was Katagiri-san who asked for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, an ofuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:31.27,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: An Ofuro are part of a Japanese ritual of bathing. They are not used for washing, but for relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body was all wet from so much sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, how nice! Really feels great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tomo, let's get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yea, ouch, ouch, ouch, ouch, ouch, ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body is already sore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:01.59,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiting already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:03.47,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't started yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:06.38,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,My stomach's hurting. I can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:09.60,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! What'll you do if that's the only thing that gets you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we were going to a beautiful studio!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:33.41,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:37.17,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that dancing and singing at the same time would be so tiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:41.09,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,You demon, You mustached demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:42.25,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,A mustached demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:45.51,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,For being a demon with a mustache, he's an Onihige.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:47.18,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:49.30,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough. Let's go to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:55.77,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I don't feel so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:58.60,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi! Are you okay?
