Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:07.95,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid thing, if you all stay best-friends, you won't survive in the professional world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:11.66,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a joke, Yumi's part of this group.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:18.12,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll all run around the lagoon until Sakaibara gets better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:19.04,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:20.29,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she from the group?
