Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:25.38,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,That one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:29.93,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a lagoon, it's a lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:32.80,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I'll go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, it's my fault that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Onihige is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi, your skin is so soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially this part, it's very soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.19,0:06:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erika!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:07:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's to know you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had that kind of relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll start in a while, Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Control your abdomen better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breathe on three.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your abdomen to do vocal exercises.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be in charge of the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Me?
