Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:07:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and prepare lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
