Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accept this wonderful lunch that I, Saya made.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:47.15,Default Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This taste...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not taste, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this food?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're joking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katagiri-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! At least he looks like he's liking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He fainted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Saya-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all have blue faces...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of Katagiri-san's infernal training, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this lunch looks tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Saya make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next opportunity we get, how about we write that your speciality is culinary on your profile?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saya-chan, you can't lie on your profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katagiri Hitoshi and Erika Campbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought together really interesting members.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like Onihige much, Katagiri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He only wants to stress us more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.93,0:10:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like he hates music.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he's trying to make us quit singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be novice's massacre?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Kogure-san and Keiko-san are being fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:11:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want someone who doesn't like music, recording Yui-senpai's music.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's throw him out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will, it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every human is afraid of spirits and ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's common all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's even common for spirits to be in a recording studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, we'll scare him and make him go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look too scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miru, I told you to get rid of that plushie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds  like he's sharpening something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be a knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is Onihige really a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we get in, we'll all scream, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-don't go near him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? It's really a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katagiri-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't sleep with all the noisey wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:13:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's wrong everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miki-senpai, we're not keeping up with that director's strong rhythm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foreign magazines?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Katagiri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this magazine also.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a special on Katagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this famous magazine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We knew that Katagiri-san was an amazing person,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it looks like he hates music.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can only imagine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katagiri-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an irritating man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he say "That's nonsense!"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he didn't hear us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five, four, three, two, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.18,0:14:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the other three?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they're not feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we let it be like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it doesn't matter if we take that nonsense training.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't keep up with anymore of Katagiri-san's training.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a reporter of an artistic magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kousaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From today until the last day, he'll collect information about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you slack off, he'll even take photos of you slacking, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, we won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:14:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saya-chan, get closer to Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, now we'll take photos of each one, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomo-chan first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tomo! You're a professional, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is different from Onihige's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomo-chan, pretend you're singing in the microphone, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomo, Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new Lemon Angels are really good friends, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm anxious for your debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really anxious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.24,0:15:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tomo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, the last one is Erika-chan. Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm ready to do any pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the way you look, Erika-chan doesn't look too much like Takumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some time ago, I had an interview with your brother, Takumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're siblings, Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We are..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't look alike?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People say that a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:38.03,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:39.37,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:41.37,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:43.58,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Why that sad face?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:45.75,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui, say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:48.01,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:49.96,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:16:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can finally return it to Katagiri now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "What're we going to do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About killing the training.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so down?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening! You're having a secret meeting so late a night?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, you want to see the photos from today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show us, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's talk about something other than work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other than work?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Katagiri-san's old stories, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, the reason why director Katagiri's going abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To test his own power?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, after losing his power in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five years ago, Katagiri Hitoshi destroyed the throat of Japanese music's precious princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:17:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know of the name Alice, at least?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That singer who appeared like the wind and retired the very next year?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katagiri was Alice's producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He destroyed an incredible singer like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're also in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a troubling producer and a big dark fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two scandals together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A big dark fact?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Famous group,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:34.63,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Takumi Meaning. | Living With His Beloved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi's living with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's also a fact about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:37.63,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,The partner is a Lemon Angel member - Erika Campbell!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by living together?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're siblings, a family!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two don't have the same blood, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not true siblings, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Troublesome director and Takumi's partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And attention to the debut music of the new Lemon Angel. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that scandal comes up, it may produce several interesting things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, me and Takumi don't have the same blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't mean we have that kind of relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a family!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nowadays, nobody looks for the truth, impact is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice of you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a good interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi is the only one I need now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having an interview with someone that hasn't got your family's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he finds out...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erika, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erika!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Katagiri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Already been five years, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.41,0:20:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five years ago,thanks to you,a really interesting story came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Producer steals Byba's song."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was really true?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were still in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think I had completely vanished?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time I didn't know what to do after losing my job, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to tell you why I still work in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To avenge you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kousaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi is an orphan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father and mother adopted Takumi when he was a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:21:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Takumi doesn't know that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something he needs to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we don't have the same blood, we've always lived like a family up to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to find Takumi quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't, Erika.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erika-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erika, if you go now, you'll be disqualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.56,0:21:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this isn't the moment to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.48,0:21:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miki-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls, we have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:38.43,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I woke up, her bags weren't there anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really went to Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that means that she's disqualified?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.12,0:22:07.80,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\an8}hajimete negatta hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.12,0:22:07.80,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Since the first day i laid eyes on you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.15,0:22:16.14,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\an8}nazeka kokoro ga nemuren nakunatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.15,0:22:16.14,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}For some reason my heart can't seem to rest
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:24.90,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\an8}denwa wa suru yuuki mo nai kawari
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:24.90,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}I don't have the courage to pick up the phone and call.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:34.79,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\an8}toomawari guuzen wo kiri
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:34.79,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Please, if for only a chance
