Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.21,0:22:39.71,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}When girls
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.86,0:22:43.50,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\an8}koi wo suru ta bi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.86,0:22:43.50,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}are in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.72,0:22:49.66,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\an8}sabishigari ni naru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.72,0:22:49.66,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}...They become lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.69,0:22:52.45,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\an8}itsudaatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.69,0:22:52.45,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}As they do.
