Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.05,0:23:11.67,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Girls in Love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.77,0:23:18.62,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\an8}Motto dakishimete yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.77,0:23:18.62,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Hold me closer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.63,0:23:28.36,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\an8}Yume no naka made tsuretette
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.63,0:23:28.36,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}and take me to a world I can only dream about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:33.39,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)\an7}Next Time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.37,0:23:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a joke that Erika was disqualified, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.12,0:23:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister was disqualified from Lemon Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.09,0:23:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you feel about Erika, Takumi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.71,0:23:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A love thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.33,0:23:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really love each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.21,0:23:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.96,0:23:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.30,0:23:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Lemon Angel Project, episode 9, "Symphony of Sorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.63,0:23:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want Erika to be disqualified!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.10,0:23:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand the conversation.

